Scramble up the boulders to the east end of the Perch (past

Left Handed Jew

). Locate a semi-circular crack (this route is Circle Jerk).  Lack Crack starts up the right side of Circle Jerk.  You can either start in a hole below the crack or walk around a boulder to start at the crack.  To descend scramble up, walk right then scramble down boulders to your start.

